Software Testing Life Cycle (STLC):
Is Structured step-step process for testing software to enure it meets both Business and Tecnical.
1. Requirement Analysis: spcification application architecutre document.
2.Test planning: create a detailed plan for testing a software applicationor product.
3.Test case development: create a detailed step- by-step instructionsfor testing an application or product.
4.Environment setup: checking all the require software,hardware,internet etc.
5.Test Execution:it is the process of running the test and cases.
6.Test cycle closure:it is  final phase of the testing process.
